51199fdea64008cc223787145e43e994bbc37fe","tid":204724,"uid":76249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99869176f3df4086dcefeb7e043605fdcad0f73","tid":204724,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌，炒樓港蝗整死左香港<br />\n依家又想搞日本<br />\n<br />\n死撚開啦，港蝗</blockquote><br />\n放心啦，日本樓市冇可能炒得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港豬快啲買日本樓啦，投資高回報㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個㗎仔朋友話勁多吉屋，佢住個區已經係年輕中產區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己去過日本 2 次,我知自己淨係在 7-11, family mart 比錢收銀已經唔知點算,同埋日本人在生活上用好多野分開外地人......在咁的地方我自問生存唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaa29d799225687cd1a3dbbd08a18d836020a5f","tid":204724,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"住係基本權利，炒樓真係好陰質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747b7e956bf037758daf99d6dcda0237de77083f","tid":204724,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"以前睇叮噹<br />\n<br />\n大雄成間House都俾人叫窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cd0bc79716c4cbfcd64fe2909b31cba63e0084","tid":204724,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，炒樓港蝗整死左香港<br />\n依家又想搞日本<br />\n<br />\n死撚開啦，港蝗</blockquote><br />\n放心啦，日本樓市冇可能炒得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港豬快啲買日本樓啦，投資高回報㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本買樓好似跟居留或入藉無關吧?"},{"pid":"03363d92ccce39cd818486366beb7eaca0690596","tid":204724,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/In95wHcnwJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIn95wHcnwJY&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2377818a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/In95wHcnwJY</a></blockquote><br />\n香港日本都無人工加，但日本樓價租金越來越平，香港就越來越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23604bf5d1673e5615f11d66b6a19a09810fe945","tid":204724,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"以為講緊果個ipad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25248570c8a7a5553b299eed5341618805f9e78c","tid":204724,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，炒樓港蝗整死左香港<br />\n依家又想搞日本<br />\n<br />\n死撚開啦，港蝗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n皇軍不會比支那人得手,放心!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大和民族冇咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad8349601261d9b787ba90a0b60935343ef6147","tid":204724,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4065f0bcf6507843d91e1339fb9761f2bd6cdfac","tid":204724,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"留名等睇"},{"pid":"f6c05119468d393078eae1c9f5478355c4c42cd9","tid":204724,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"咁香港幾時爆呀屌"},{"pid":"51da46b1e1b24613bf770d75fd2361f403fd4f67","tid":204724,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:43:04.000